# Hand-written sample trace -- exercises every line form the reader accepts.
# Sequential fill of a small region.
W 0
W 1
W 2
W 3
W 4
W 5
W 6
W 7

# Bare LPNs are writes too.
8
9
10
11

# Read back what we just wrote (reads do not consume physical pages).
R 0
R 4
R 11

# Repeated overwrite of one hot page: every line here invalidates the previous
# copy and programs a fresh physical page, so this alone drives GC.
W 3
W 3
W 3
W 3
W 3
W 3
W 3
W 3

# A read of a page that was never written -- resolves to unmapped.
R 900

# Scattered writes across the region.
W 12
W 5
W 19
W 2
W 27
W 8
W 31
W 14
W 3
W 22

# Lowercase op letters are accepted as well.
w 6
r 6
